  "detailed_description": "\"Vtuber Simulator\" developed by a one-person independent development team RA Studio.<br />\r\nCustomize your own character, streaming, training, and become a famous Vtuber!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【Game Introduction】<br />\r\nIt’s an era when everyone wants to be a Vtuber,<br />\r\nThe protagonist wants to be a famous Vtuber!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【Game Features】<br />\r\n-Customized character system!<br />\r\n-Easy and happy story<br />\r\n-Train yourself to make the live broadcast more interesting.<br />\r\n-Solve the problems encountered during the live broadcast<br />\r\n-Edit and upload videos to get the most authentic reply!<br />\r\n-If the target fails, you can inherit the attributes and start again!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHi, everyone !<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI am RA studio game producer Ryan ,from a one-man studio. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n\"Vtuber Simulator\" was made in my spare time alone.<br />\r\nI really like the culture of Vtuber, so i made this.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTranslating into a language other than Chinese is very hard, there may be problems, please leave a message for advice.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHope everyone will like it.",
  "about_the_game": "\"Vtuber Simulator\" developed by a one-person independent development team RA Studio.<br />\r\nCustomize your own character, streaming, training, and become a famous Vtuber!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【Game Introduction】<br />\r\nIt’s an era when everyone wants to be a Vtuber,<br />\r\nThe protagonist wants to be a famous Vtuber!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【Game Features】<br />\r\n-Customized character system!<br />\r\n-Easy and happy story<br />\r\n-Train yourself to make the live broadcast more interesting.<br />\r\n-Solve the problems encountered during the live broadcast<br />\r\n-Edit and upload videos to get the most authentic reply!<br />\r\n-If the target fails, you can inherit the attributes and start again!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHi, everyone !<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI am RA studio game producer Ryan ,from a one-man studio. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n\"Vtuber Simulator\" was made in my spare time alone.<br />\r\nI really like the culture of Vtuber, so i made this.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTranslating into a language other than Chinese is very hard, there may be problems, please leave a message for advice.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHope everyone will like it.",
